          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop the<strong> carrots</strong> into batons</p><p>Add the <strong>carrot batons</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiling water</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 1 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2000.-step-5-x200.jpg",
