    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the <strong>green beans</strong>, then add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and <strong>trimmed</strong> <strong>green beans </strong>and cook for a further 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the vegetables and return them to the pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
