      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>breaded fish</strong> with the <strong>chips</strong>,<strong> vegetables</strong> and <strong>lemony mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
